</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1>Etched Earring of Veracity</h1><br>by Gemdiver of Fennin Ro</center><br><div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="573" id="AutoNumber1">
